      <title>T. Rowe 表示绿色债券对美国发行人的吸引力正在下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/t-rowe-says-green-bonds-becoming-less-appealing-for-us-issuers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[普信集团 (T. Rowe Price Group Inc.) 的马特·劳顿 (Matt Lawton) 表示，美国环保债券的发行量可能仍将维持低迷，因为企业出售此类债券不再获得实质性的价格优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/t-rowe-says-green-bonds-becoming-less-appealing-for-us-issuers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 17:14:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
